(2216, 226, 'about_content', 'Shiloh Church was founded by Pastor Raj Dass and Pastor Namita Dass with Pastor Robert McLure, in 2010. Pastor Raj serves Shiloh Church as the Lead Pastor and Pastor Namita leads in the church administration and Discipleship in the church. Pastor Robert dedicates his time with Shiloh Church, in strengthening congregation spiritually. Pastor Emmanuel Khadam is a senior pastor, and he serves the congregation with his vast experience. Shiloh Church exists, to impart Spiritual insights to help people to be established in Faith in Lord Jesus Christ. We are currently located in Mississauga, Canada.'),
