(3196, 293, 'about_content', 'Shiloh International Church Canada was founded by Pastor Raj Dass, Pastor Namita Dass, Pastor Robert Maclure and Asif Sohail in 2010.\r\n\r\nPastor Raj is the Lead Pastor of the Church. Pastor Namita leads the church discipleship and administration of the church.\r\n\r\nPastor Robert dedicates his time to strengthening the congregation spiritually.\r\nPastor Emmanuel Khadam is a senior pastor, he serves the congregation with his vast experience, in Evangelism and Prayer.\r\nShiloh Church exists, to impart Spiritual insights, and to help people be established in their Faith in the Lord Jesus Christ.'),
