(325, 1, '2023-11-30 14:13:40', '2023-11-30 14:13:40', 'My name is Shilendra. I was suffering from prostrate problems. I was treated by the specialists doctors. I was given medicines and put a bag on me. Because of this I was feeling very weak and I was very uncomfortable to go out. As such, we were not able to come to the church and I was not able to go to my job.We all prayed at home and I called pastor for prayers. Pastor Raj and pastor Namita visited our home and prayed with us according to James 5:13-15. I am very happy to say that in the next few days, I was healed and the doctors said that I don’t need any external bag. The pain has reduced completely. Next week, I am returning to work. All glory to God.', 'Brother Shailendra', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brother-shailendra', '', '', '2023-12-04 06:01:53', '2023-12-04 06:01:53', '', 0, 'https://creativeproapp.com/development/shiloh-church/?post_type=testimoni&#038;p=325', 0, 'testimoni', '', 0),
