(329, 1, '2023-11-30 14:27:51', '2023-11-30 14:27:51', 'My name is Shilendra. I was suffering from prostrate problems. I was treated by the\nspecialists doctors. I was given medicines and put a bag on me. Because of this I was\nfeeling very weak and I was very uncomfortable to go out. As such, we were not able to\ncome to the church and I was not able to go to my job.\nWe all prayed at home and I called pastor for prayers. Pastor Raj and pastor Namita\nvisited our home and prayed with us according to James 5:13-15.\nI am very happy to say that in the next few days, I was healed and the doctors said that\nI don’t need any external bag. The pain has reduced completely. Next week, I am\nreturning to work. All glory to God.', 'Brother Shailendra', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '325-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-11-30 14:27:51', '2023-11-30 14:27:51', '', 325, 'https://creativeproapp.com/development/shiloh-church/?p=329', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
