(333, 1, '2023-12-04 05:59:50', '2023-12-04 05:59:50', 'My son and daughter-in -law are married for 13 years. After many years of marriage,they didn’t have a baby. We tried medical treatments from different doctors but nothing worked.We sent a prayer request to Shiloh Church and pastor Raj prayed for my son and his wife over phone. We are happy to testify that this year, we are blessed with a baby girl after 13 years of marriage of my son. We thank our Lord Jesus Christ for His blessings.', 'Sister Stella Yadav', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sister-stella-yadav', '', '', '2023-12-04 06:14:44', '2023-12-04 06:14:44', '', 0, 'https://creativeproapp.com/development/shiloh-church/?post_type=testimoni&#038;p=333', 0, 'testimoni', '', 0),
(334, 1, '2023-12-04 06:00:59', '2023-12-04 06:00:59', 'My name is Ezra Anand. I got married in January this year and moved to Germany.After coming here, we tried for a job in this new country. My German language skills are very limited and I have no previous experience in the industry in Germany.We sent a prayer request to Shiloh Church to pray for my job and settlement in\r\nGermany. I am very happy to bring this praise report that, I have got a good job in my field in a multinational company here. We as a family, want to give all glory to God for His provisions in our lives. Hallelujah.', 'Ezra Anand', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ezra-anand', '', '', '2023-12-04 06:00:59', '2023-12-04 06:00:59', '', 0, 'https://creativeproapp.com/development/shiloh-church/?post_type=testimoni&#038;p=334', 0, 'testimoni', '', 0),
